{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/PlatformerEN.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br>In this <strong>platformer unlike any you\u2019ve seen before</strong>, you\u2019re gonna have to learn to manage your lives like a true demon !<br>It\u2019s no big deal, only a few <strong>seconds long levels</strong> to run through.<br><br>Although, down under here, <strong>contracts</strong> are everything and you\u2019re going to have to work with it\u2026<br>And in the underworld, when you make a pact, you need to <strong>take responsibility</strong>!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/Satanislas_contrats_vid.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/ShopEN.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br><strong>Jumping, rolling, gliding</strong>, that\u2019s all good and dandy\u2026 But let\u2019s be honest: without my <strong>demonic shop</strong>, where the <strong>only valid currency is your lives</strong>, you stand no chance of overcoming <strong>the Ossuary</strong>!<br>Or even <strong>the Abyss</strong>.<br>Nor <strong>the Inferno</strong>\u2026<br>You have no shot in <strong>Evil Industries</strong>!<br>Don\u2019t even think of clearing <strong>Chateau Satan</strong>!!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/Satanislas_shop_bonus.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br>All these <strong>bonuses and curses</strong> available in the shop, if you\u2019re willing to <strong>spend or gain lives</strong>, define the <strong>difficulty you set up for yourself</strong> on the current level. Put it simply: you\u2019re <strong>betting with yourself</strong> that you\u2019ll succeed with no bonus, or even with a few curses\u2026 or not! (I\u2019m betting on the latter)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/Satanislas_shop_malus.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/CourageEN.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br>Anyway\u2026 let\u2019s <i>suppose</i> you actually make it (unlikely), you\u2019ll still need enough stamina and bravery to <strong>take things with a new angle and attempt speedrunning</strong>!<br>Know what I mean? Dodging <strong>spikes</strong>, outsmarting <strong>minions</strong>, leap over <strong>sticky tar</strong>, overcome <strong>giant blade traps</strong>, and so on, to finally <strong>beat the creator\u2019s best times</strong>. Just thinking that you might ever achieve this makes me laugh!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171680/extras/Satanislas_Speedrun.gif?t=1706539888\" /><br><br>I mean, there\u2019s over <strong>50 levels</strong>. Quite a lot of <strong>replayability</strong> too, depending on what you\u2019re going to pick from the shop!<br>No bragging, but we did manage to make high level speedrunners rage during playtesting.<br>A few of those even shed some tears\u2026<br><br>And if you think you\u2019re done after a single run, we\u2019ve got plenty of other contracts waiting to be signed, with some spicy <strong>new challenges added to all those levels</strong>!<br><br>Don\u2019t worry, we won\u2019t mind if you\u2019re ready to give up on the very first level.<br>Just, maybe, don\u2019t mention it to your friends, it <i>is</i> the tutorial after all\u2026","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Contracted","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2171680/ab1efdd4ad326fcae0605e5d5b723215cc669b90.jpg"},{"name":"Master of paperwork","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2171680/057c9fd2dac25